{"tid":1452404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(請廣傳) 低成本高效益抗爭方法","createTime":"2019-08-12T01:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:18:35.000Z","uid":272778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b23a7c9b20c3db6b6f89cf27ceed9b8be76142d","tid":1452404,"uid":272778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:08:15.000Z","msg":"[金融反擊擊]<br />\n<br />\n作為一個已經有家室既中佬, 請原諒我不能走上前線; 不過金融界既一份仔, 如果大家同我一樣咁嬲既話, 可以考慮:<br />\n<br />\n1. 將強積金中既中港股票投資, 轉走到其他地區 (例如歐美), 反正中港股巿都係一潭死水, 到現在都未重返07年新高 (美國2013年已破07年高位)。請唔好睇少呢個行為, 直至2019年3月, 香港既強積金規模已經去到接近9萬億港元。而香港股巿一日既成交頂多都係一千億。<br />\n<br />\n2. 提走中資銀行既儲蓄戶口儲款, 要開都去滙豐/恒生/渣打開。<br />\n<br />\n3. 如果有保險喺中資保險公司, 可以既話請轉去非中資公司。<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果有樓按, 過左罰息期, 請轉按到非中資銀行。<br />\n<br />\n5. 停止再投資任何中資IPO // 債券"},{"pid":"b61062c13f950194d406bfdac4a6760578a95657","tid":1452404,"uid":272778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afd5518ba0c0e8451eb005ff6f0b271a4de860a","tid":1452404,"uid":272778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bace2bd034ad4cb1240860694efa49c6f8f463cd","tid":1452404,"uid":272778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7824a3fd4583047f03e21d518320df31190801","tid":1452404,"uid":272778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c9f038146b98122bd7603ca7756f95eced6882","tid":1452404,"uid":272778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f93f4e7a0e4c3e1bd17d523e76df89d5a37ad0","tid":145240